n, m = map(int, input().split())
    a = list(map(int, input().split()))
    a.sort()
    a = a[::-1]
    res = []
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(i+1, n):
            if (a[i] + a[j]) % m not in res:
                res.append((a[i] + a[j]) % m)
    res.sort()
    print(len(res))
    print(*res)
